calculateSpaceGroupMultiplicity

public int calculateSpaceGroupMultiplicity(CMLSymmetry symmetry)
calculate the spaceGroup multiplicity of the atom. this is defined by attribute spaceGroupMultiplicity and is the number of symmetry operators that transform the atom onto itself with normalization of cell translations.

Parameters:
symmetry - spaceGroup operators
Returns:
the multiplicity (0 if no coordinates else 1 or more)
